{"word":"ἀρτίφρων","slug":"ἀρτίφρων","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀρτίφρων</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ἄρτιος, φρήν</el>\n<p/><i>sound of mind, sensible</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>: <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <el>γάμων</el> <i>fully conscious</i> of a thing, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/>"}]}